# ðŸ§¾ Backend - Product Management System


- User authentication (JWT access & refresh tokens)
- OTP verification (via Nodemailer)
- Profile management (Able to block another users to prevent seeing our profile data)
- Blocking system
- Brand and Product management (with filtering/sorting)
-Built using Clean Architecture for separation of concerns and maintainability


- Node.js + Express.js
- MongoDB + Mongoose
- TypeScript
- JWT (access & refresh tokens)
- bcryptjs (password hashing)
- nodemailer (OTP email verification)




1. Clone the repo:

git clone https://github.com/Shanushajahan707/productApplication.git
cd backend


2. Install dependencies:

npm install


3. Create `.env` file:

PORT=5000
MONGODB_URI=<your-mongo-uri>
JWT_SECRET=<jwt-secret>
REFRESH_SECRET=<refresh-token-secret>
EMAIL_USER=<your-email> 
EMAIL_PASS=<your-email-password>
```

4. Start the server:

npm run dev


